 <arm>
   <uof name="Parameterization_and_variational_representation">
     <description>
The Parameterization_and_variational_representation UoF specifies the data structure for the high level description of operations to modify 
solids by local shape operations. The basic modification operations are defined in the 
application modules which reference this module. This module provides a mechanism for associating a base solid with the solid 
resulting from the application of a shape modification operation. it also provides for the definition of a sequence of 
modification operations.
  </description>

